WEBVTT

00:01.369 --> 00:03.537
ANNOUNCER: Thanks for
downloading this Fox show.

00:03.571 --> 00:05.739
And don't miss
all-new episodes on Fox.

00:07.941 --> 00:10.144
Previously on Empire...
Loretha.

00:10.178 --> 00:11.645
Barry...
Come to get my girl.

00:11.679 --> 00:13.847
Just so we're clear,
she's mine.

00:13.881 --> 00:16.184
JAMAL: I decided to hold off
on the release of
When Cookie Met Lucious.

00:16.217 --> 00:17.585
I'm gonna join
Dad's show in Vegas.

00:17.618 --> 00:19.553
COOKIE:
Giuliana is a cancer,

00:19.587 --> 00:22.523
and if we don't root
that bitch out, we all die.

00:22.556 --> 00:24.358
ANDRE: Charlotte is deadly
serious about

00:24.392 --> 00:25.993
keeping the thug element
out of Vegas.

00:26.026 --> 00:27.828
We'll just have to give her

00:27.861 --> 00:30.564
Biggie and 'Pac times ten.

00:30.598 --> 00:32.833
Mama, what did you do?
They ruined one of mine,

00:32.866 --> 00:34.868
so I took one of theirs.

00:34.902 --> 00:37.571
Wait till you find out
where I found Bella.

00:40.908 --> 00:42.910
*

00:47.248 --> 00:48.782
* Players *

00:48.816 --> 00:51.819
* Put yo' pinky rings
up to the moon *

00:53.587 --> 00:56.490
* Girls, what y'all
tryin' to do? *

00:57.758 --> 00:59.593
* 24-karat magic *

00:59.627 --> 01:03.697
* In the air *

01:03.731 --> 01:05.633
* Head to toe, so, player *

01:05.666 --> 01:06.667
* Uh, look out! *

01:08.602 --> 01:10.371
* Pop pop, it's show time *
* Show time

01:10.404 --> 01:11.472
* Show time *
* Show time

01:11.505 --> 01:13.641
* Guess who's back again *

01:13.674 --> 01:15.709
* Oh, they don't know? *
* Go on, tell 'em

01:15.743 --> 01:17.645
* I bet they know soon
as we walk in *
* Showin' up

01:17.678 --> 01:19.113
* Wearing Cuban links *
* Yeah

01:19.147 --> 01:21.081
* Designer minks *
* Yeah

01:21.115 --> 01:22.916
* Inglewood's finest shoes *
* Whoop, whoop

01:22.950 --> 01:24.652
* Don't look too hard
might hurt ya'self *

01:24.685 --> 01:26.387
* Known to give the color red
the blues *

01:26.420 --> 01:28.322
Welcome to Vegas,
big-daddy style.

01:28.356 --> 01:29.323
(shrieks)

01:29.357 --> 01:31.459
Welcome to Vegas, baby!

01:31.492 --> 01:33.161
Hey, put my mama
on the phone.

01:33.194 --> 01:35.696
Yes, sir.
(clears throat)

01:36.864 --> 01:37.931
(toilet flushes)

01:37.965 --> 01:38.966
It's Mr. Lyon.

01:40.934 --> 01:43.604
Dwight? How long
do you plan on

01:43.637 --> 01:45.439
keeping me cooped up
in here?

01:45.473 --> 01:47.741
You're gonna stay in there
until you're no longer

01:47.775 --> 01:49.677
having this episode
you're having.

01:49.710 --> 01:51.312
I'm not having an episode.

01:51.345 --> 01:54.182
I put steel in the skull
of your enemy.

01:54.215 --> 01:56.450
You know what, I don't know
what you're talking about,

01:56.484 --> 01:58.319
and I'm sure
you don't either.

01:58.352 --> 01:59.987
Take your medication.

02:00.020 --> 02:02.623
Juanita will tell me
when you're under control.

02:02.656 --> 02:04.225
(scoffs)

02:06.059 --> 02:07.761
Thank you.

02:07.795 --> 02:11.299
You know, it's not sanitary
to keep that in here.

02:29.583 --> 02:32.052
JAMAL: Oh, my goodness, Ma, you
just need to, like, cut it.

02:32.085 --> 02:33.354
You know what I'm saying?
You know why I'm doing it.

02:33.387 --> 02:36.156
Mm-mm, I can't.

02:36.190 --> 02:40.328
Shoot, maybe because
your devilish father

02:40.361 --> 02:42.863
tricked you into pulling
When Cookie Met Lucious

02:42.896 --> 02:44.698
so Inferno could get ahead.

02:44.732 --> 02:46.567
Ma, it's not some sort
of conspiracy.

02:46.600 --> 02:49.136
If I do Inferno, then that'll
get the fans excited

02:49.169 --> 02:51.071
for When Cookie Met Lucious
actually drops.

02:51.104 --> 02:53.474
Dad knows that, I know that,
you should know that, too.

02:53.507 --> 02:55.509
What does Giuliana have
to say, huh?

02:55.543 --> 02:57.010
Who...
Did she put her two cents in?

02:57.044 --> 02:58.512
You know this is
all her idea.

02:58.546 --> 02:59.913
Once she gets rid of me,

02:59.947 --> 03:01.048
she coming after you
and your brothers.

03:01.081 --> 03:02.650
Trust me on that.
Oh, my Lord.

03:02.683 --> 03:04.318
Ma, first of all I don't
deal with that woman.

03:04.352 --> 03:06.520
Second of all, she has
no sort of power

03:06.554 --> 03:07.821
to get rid of you.

03:07.855 --> 03:10.724
You Cookie Lyon, Ma.
Like, come on.

03:10.758 --> 03:12.360
Just come to the show.

03:12.393 --> 03:15.062
I can't, the bitch
had me black-booked.

03:15.095 --> 03:18.198
Yeah, If I go anywhere near
Laviticus Vegas... (chuckles)

03:18.232 --> 03:19.733
the cameras will
recognize my face

03:19.767 --> 03:21.835
and set off the alarms--
ain't that some bull?

03:21.869 --> 03:23.070
Yeah, that is some bull.

03:23.103 --> 03:25.539
Look, you ain't got to worry
about that, all right?

03:25.573 --> 03:29.042
I'll talk to Dad.
Just come to the show.

03:29.076 --> 03:30.444
Yeah, you do that.

03:30.478 --> 03:32.513
I'm only coming to see
you perform, anyway.

03:32.546 --> 03:34.214
That's the only reason
you should be coming.

03:34.248 --> 03:35.616
(both laugh)

03:37.117 --> 03:38.786
You think you could also

03:38.819 --> 03:40.754
get Hakeem to come, you
know what I'm saying?

03:40.788 --> 03:42.790
He don't need to be
by himself here and...

03:42.823 --> 03:45.092
I mean, we tried to convince him
to come be in the show, but...

03:45.125 --> 03:47.761
His head ain't been in the game
since Bella went missing.

03:47.795 --> 03:50.931
Don't you worry about that,
though, I will take care of him.

03:50.964 --> 03:52.366
I'm not gonna leave him
by hisself, you know that.

03:52.400 --> 03:54.201
I know.

03:54.234 --> 03:58.071
* Get it back to the Tri-State *

03:58.105 --> 04:00.073
* That's the rocket launcher
or that golden Smithen *

04:00.107 --> 04:01.775
* Smith and Wesson, it'll
eject ya, golden hit ya... *

04:01.809 --> 04:03.043
Nothing works, so I'm gonna
try it my way.

04:03.076 --> 04:05.379
Get off the phone!

04:05.413 --> 04:06.747
You're not gonna
find Bella by

04:06.780 --> 04:08.048
releasing a bunch of
idiots on the street.

04:08.081 --> 04:11.218
Whoa. Who you calling
an idiot?

04:11.251 --> 04:13.721
Right. We the new wave, mama.
This is how we do.

04:13.754 --> 04:15.255
This is reckless.

04:15.289 --> 04:16.724
Okay, Hakeem, you guys
have already completely

04:16.757 --> 04:18.692
vandalized the DuBois...
I don't care!

04:20.994 --> 04:21.962
(phone ringing,
Anika sighs)

04:21.995 --> 04:24.164
Give me a second.

04:24.197 --> 04:25.599
Let's go, people

04:25.633 --> 04:26.734
Hello?

04:26.767 --> 04:28.235
Oh, hello, dear.

04:28.268 --> 04:30.070
It's your soon-to-be
ex-mother-in-law.

04:30.103 --> 04:31.104
ANIKA:
What do you want?

04:31.138 --> 04:32.340
I want you to come

04:32.373 --> 04:34.408
and get rid of your
things, Boo Boo.

04:34.442 --> 04:36.510
I don't want to be reminded
you ever existed.

04:36.544 --> 04:38.178
Besides,

04:38.211 --> 04:39.647
you have a whole pile of mail.

04:39.680 --> 04:40.648
Unless you want me
to start opening it.

04:40.681 --> 04:41.915
Don't touch it.

04:41.949 --> 04:43.283
I will be back
as soon as I can.

04:43.317 --> 04:45.553
All righty.
I'll be expecting you.

04:48.722 --> 04:50.090
Turn it around.

04:50.123 --> 04:52.593
(Anika sighs)

04:52.626 --> 04:55.629
Look, Hakeem, listen.

04:55.663 --> 04:57.431
I know that you're
worried, I'm worried, too.

04:57.465 --> 05:01.535
But don't be crazy, like your
grandmother, all right?

05:01.569 --> 05:03.471
I know that
Bella's all right.

05:03.504 --> 05:04.605
I can...

05:04.638 --> 05:06.507
I can feel it.

05:06.540 --> 05:07.875
Trust me.

05:19.387 --> 05:21.889
* How lucky can one guy be? *

05:21.922 --> 05:24.658
* I kissed her
and she kissed me... *

05:24.692 --> 05:27.495
CHARLOTTE:
Wow, the venue is amazing.

05:27.528 --> 05:31.164
I can't wait to see Inferno
light up this space.

05:31.198 --> 05:33.901
Now, there is one thing
I'd like to share

05:33.934 --> 05:35.335
with both of you.

05:35.369 --> 05:39.707
September 7, 1996.

05:39.740 --> 05:42.976
Yes. That would be the
day that Tupac was shot.

05:43.010 --> 05:44.678
You know your
Vegas history.

05:44.712 --> 05:45.846
Well, actually, Charlotte,

05:45.879 --> 05:47.748
she knows her
hip-hop history.

05:47.781 --> 05:49.850
Well, that's semantics.

05:49.883 --> 05:53.153
In any case, earlier
that evening,

05:53.186 --> 05:55.222
Mr. Shakur and
Mr. Suge Knight

05:55.255 --> 05:57.825
and a gang of their
gangster friends

05:57.858 --> 05:59.893
stomped out their
rival in the lobby

05:59.927 --> 06:01.328
of the MGM Grand.

06:01.361 --> 06:04.898
My father was gaming
commissioner back then,

06:04.932 --> 06:07.868
and he lost his job
because of those vile thugs.

06:07.901 --> 06:10.538
If there's any ruckus

06:10.571 --> 06:13.106
on the opening night
of Inferno,

06:13.140 --> 06:15.876
it'll be the last time Empire
sets foot on the Strip.

06:20.113 --> 06:23.250
Hmm...
Hmm, she told you.

06:23.283 --> 06:24.217
She told you.

06:24.251 --> 06:26.219
(both laugh)

06:28.922 --> 06:32.359
ANDRE: I ran the plan
by Cookie, she's on board.

06:32.392 --> 06:33.861
When the show starts,
ten of our people

06:33.894 --> 06:35.729
will be positioned
inside the theater.

06:35.763 --> 06:38.098
We count down, another ten or
12 will bust through the door,

06:38.131 --> 06:39.232
and all hell breaks loose.

06:39.266 --> 06:41.268
Cookie said no fireworks,

06:41.301 --> 06:42.770
just boots and bats.

06:42.803 --> 06:45.272
She's just worried about
Jamal and his PTSD.

06:45.305 --> 06:46.974
Whatever. If I can
live through bipolar,

06:47.007 --> 06:49.042
he can live through this.

06:49.076 --> 06:50.711
When it's all said and
done, we'll be positioned

06:50.744 --> 06:52.946
to take over the lease
and start our own

06:52.980 --> 06:55.549
independent venture in Vegas.

06:55.583 --> 06:57.485
You tell Cookie about
the final piece of the plan?

06:57.518 --> 07:00.220
Hell no. No matter
what he does to her,

07:00.253 --> 07:02.790
she'll always be
in love with him.

07:02.823 --> 07:05.092
You really hate him, huh?

07:05.125 --> 07:06.326
(Andre chuckles)

07:06.359 --> 07:07.461
SHINE:
What'd he do to you?

07:08.962 --> 07:10.998
Everything.

07:11.031 --> 07:13.166
More than you could
ever imagine.

07:15.035 --> 07:18.305
I'm the only one that knows
what he truly is.

07:18.338 --> 07:19.940
That's why I got to kill him.

07:21.709 --> 07:23.744
You sure?

07:23.777 --> 07:26.179
Positive.

07:32.185 --> 07:33.954
Andre, this is Franco.

07:33.987 --> 07:35.322
He's the best there is

07:35.355 --> 07:36.857
at blowing stuff up.
Really?

07:36.890 --> 07:38.025
How come I never heard of him?

07:38.058 --> 07:39.927
You aren't supposed to hear

07:39.960 --> 07:42.129
about guys like me,
if we do our jobs right.

07:42.162 --> 07:43.430
All right,
here's the deal.

07:43.463 --> 07:44.698
While the pre-show's
getting started.

07:44.732 --> 07:46.767
Franco gets everything
ready outside.

07:46.800 --> 07:48.802
Soon as we start brawling,

07:48.836 --> 07:50.638
Lucious' security will rush him
out the back entrance,

07:50.671 --> 07:52.139
trying to protect
his ass.

07:52.172 --> 07:53.641
That's when we get him.

07:53.674 --> 07:55.543
It's remotely triggered
by this phone app,

07:55.576 --> 07:58.445
so, at the push
of a button...

07:58.478 --> 08:00.180
boom.

08:00.213 --> 08:03.651
Just like that.
Boom.

08:09.222 --> 08:11.024
I'm not going to Vegas
until I find Bella.

08:11.058 --> 08:12.560
Listen, son,
I've got it

08:12.593 --> 08:14.995
on great authority
that Bella's all right.

08:15.028 --> 08:16.029
What authority?

08:18.431 --> 08:21.334
I can't go into details
right now,

08:21.368 --> 08:23.804
but I was this close
to finding her,

08:23.837 --> 08:27.307
and then something...

08:27.340 --> 08:28.241
came up.

08:28.275 --> 08:29.242
But I haven't given up

08:29.276 --> 08:30.678
my search for her, son.

08:30.711 --> 08:31.879
Well, Grandma thinks you lyin'.

08:31.912 --> 08:34.081
No, no, don't even ever

08:34.114 --> 08:36.984
listen to anything
that your grandmother says.

08:37.017 --> 08:38.919
She is out of her
freakin' mind.

08:38.952 --> 08:40.754
Look, baby, I'm not gonna
go to Vegas

08:40.788 --> 08:42.089
if you don't go, okay?

08:42.122 --> 08:43.824
I would never leave you alone.

08:43.857 --> 08:45.325
Well, what about Anika, Ma?

08:45.358 --> 08:46.326
LUCIOUS:
Don't worry about Anika.

08:46.359 --> 08:47.928
Anika got her own mama,

08:47.961 --> 08:49.563
she's got her own daddy
to look after her.

08:49.597 --> 08:51.765
Yeah.
You worry about you.

08:51.799 --> 08:53.433
Look at this place right now.

08:53.466 --> 08:55.836
Why is she acting so calm?

08:55.869 --> 08:57.838
Like she don't even care
about Bella no more.

08:57.871 --> 09:00.407
Well, baby, women have
a certain strength

09:00.440 --> 09:02.042
when it comes to when
it comes to stuff like that.

09:02.075 --> 09:04.077
We have to stay calm,

09:04.111 --> 09:07.114
even when we don't want to,
for the sake of our children.

09:08.716 --> 09:10.450
Listen to your mama.

09:12.452 --> 09:14.788
She's very wise.

09:16.323 --> 09:19.059
But you need to take
care of you right now.
Mm-hmm.

09:27.434 --> 09:29.637
Oh, don't feel the need
to hide your joy.

09:29.670 --> 09:31.104
I'm just as happy as you

09:31.138 --> 09:34.908
to be leaving
this... hellhole and you.

09:34.942 --> 09:37.144
I'm not hiding anything.

09:37.177 --> 09:40.080
I've been dancing around
in my skivvies for days.

09:40.113 --> 09:42.282
Hmph.

09:42.315 --> 09:43.851
Why do you need those?

09:45.986 --> 09:49.456
Oh, I just figured
that maybe Lucious

09:49.489 --> 09:51.625
might want me to
take everything with me.

09:51.659 --> 09:54.261
Hmm.
Your mail.

09:54.294 --> 09:56.630
Oh, yes.

09:56.664 --> 09:58.699
Don't forget to tell
the post office you moved.

10:00.300 --> 10:03.971
I think the big one is
from your divorce lawyer.

10:04.004 --> 10:06.874
Oh, yes!
Finally.

10:10.811 --> 10:12.746
Oh, careful.

10:12.780 --> 10:14.314
You don't want to rip it,

10:14.347 --> 10:16.016
in case it's a check,
or something.

10:16.049 --> 10:18.118
Why don't you use
the letter opener?

10:27.560 --> 10:29.362
(sighs)

10:29.396 --> 10:31.965
(chuckling)

10:34.902 --> 10:36.937
Bitch.

10:36.970 --> 10:38.672
(sighs)

10:41.875 --> 10:44.211
As head of the Nevada
Gaming Commission,

10:44.244 --> 10:47.280
it is my honor to welcome
Laviticus Resort and Casino

10:47.314 --> 10:48.882
to the Las Vegas Strip.

10:48.916 --> 10:50.818
I and the NGC have been working

10:50.851 --> 10:52.485
very closely
with Lucious Lyon

10:52.519 --> 10:55.322
to ensure that Laviticus
will provide safe,

10:55.355 --> 10:57.891
enjoyable, family-friendly
entertainment

10:57.925 --> 10:59.893
to our great city.

10:59.927 --> 11:03.063
We hope that Inferno will be
Vegas's next big sensation.

11:03.096 --> 11:04.664
Thank you.
(reporters clamoring)

11:04.698 --> 11:06.166
If you have any questions,

11:06.199 --> 11:07.500
refer to the press release.

11:10.237 --> 11:13.907
Honey, why don't you, uh, go to
the car and get the kids ready?

11:13.941 --> 11:15.508
ANDRE:
Commissioner Frost.

11:15.542 --> 11:16.576
Nice to see you again.

11:16.609 --> 11:18.311
Andre, good to see you.

11:18.345 --> 11:19.512
This is my husband.

11:19.546 --> 11:20.714
Mitt Frost.
Good to meet you.

11:20.748 --> 11:22.549
Andre Lyon. Pleasure.

11:22.582 --> 11:25.819
I wasn't expecting to see you
until later in the week.

11:25.853 --> 11:27.520
I came early
in case I'm needed.

11:27.554 --> 11:31.091
Once I hammer out a deal,
I like to stay on top of it.

11:32.525 --> 11:34.394
Know what I mean, Mitt?

11:34.427 --> 11:35.863
Yes, speaking of which,

11:35.896 --> 11:37.831
we should continue
the conversation

11:37.865 --> 11:39.599
we started in my office.

11:39.632 --> 11:40.868
It's just, right now,

11:40.901 --> 11:41.935
we have to go.

11:41.969 --> 11:42.936
Our son Brigham

11:42.970 --> 11:44.004
has a soccer game.

11:44.037 --> 11:45.739
Understood.

11:45.773 --> 11:47.941
Well, pleasure
to meet you, Mitt.
You as well.

11:47.975 --> 11:49.242
Charlotte.

11:49.276 --> 11:50.277
Andre.

11:55.816 --> 11:59.019
This is the official
gaming license,

11:59.052 --> 12:01.288
we are no longer in probation.

12:03.056 --> 12:05.225
(whoops)

12:05.258 --> 12:06.693
Yeah.

12:06.726 --> 12:08.561
You kept your promise.

12:08.595 --> 12:09.696
Is this everything?

12:09.729 --> 12:10.931
Yeah. Well, I just have

12:10.964 --> 12:12.732
a couple more
signatures, and...

12:12.766 --> 12:14.734
Excuse me for a second.

12:14.768 --> 12:16.770
Of course.

12:18.738 --> 12:20.974
COOKIE: I don't even have it.
Send me the...

12:21.008 --> 12:22.475
LUCIOUS:
Excuse me.

12:22.509 --> 12:24.912
Cook.

12:24.945 --> 12:27.881
Look, um...

12:27.915 --> 12:30.083
I got you invited
to the opening of Inferno.

12:30.117 --> 12:31.785
Oh. Thought I was black-booked.

12:31.819 --> 12:33.486
I pulled some strings.

12:33.520 --> 12:36.323
I'm-a have you sit
in the V.I.P. section with Dre

12:36.356 --> 12:38.058
and Hakeem.

12:38.091 --> 12:39.459
He needs you.

12:39.492 --> 12:41.795
He needs both of us
right now, 'cause...

12:41.829 --> 12:44.664
I don't know if we're gonna find
that little girl.

12:48.201 --> 12:49.736
I can't have you
backstage though.

12:49.769 --> 12:51.271
Bitch's rules?

12:51.304 --> 12:52.505
Look, I just don't want
any trouble, Cook,

12:52.539 --> 12:54.474
this is a big move
for the company.

12:54.507 --> 12:56.243
I mean, we're thinking
about franchising

12:56.276 --> 12:59.112
Laviticus clubs
all around the world,

12:59.146 --> 13:01.514
so I'm talking about
a global Empire.

13:01.548 --> 13:04.717
Right. So who gonna sit
on the throne with you?

13:10.657 --> 13:12.792
Get out of my face, Lucious.

13:27.140 --> 13:30.643
* She make that thang go drip
drop, drip drippity drop... *

13:30.677 --> 13:32.946
Hey.

13:32.980 --> 13:35.883
Hey, boo.
I know exactly who
you should date next.

13:35.916 --> 13:37.450
It needs to be, like,
a dope-ass businessman,

13:37.484 --> 13:39.019
not, like, an artist.

13:39.052 --> 13:40.854
Like, we're both done
with artists forever.

13:40.888 --> 13:43.490
