* Finally found *

27:52.104 --> 27:54.306
* This dream I *

27:54.340 --> 27:56.843
* Can dream on *

27:58.277 --> 27:59.578
* With you *

27:59.611 --> 28:00.880
* Dream on *

28:00.913 --> 28:02.414
* With you *

28:02.448 --> 28:04.851
* With you *
* Dream on *

28:04.884 --> 28:06.986
* With you *

28:07.019 --> 28:08.721
* Dream on with you. *

28:08.755 --> 28:10.422
(cheering and applause)

28:14.026 --> 28:15.995
(cheering and applause
continues)

28:16.028 --> 28:17.596
I love you, Mom.

28:17.629 --> 28:19.198
WOMAN:
That's a lot, baby!

28:19.231 --> 28:21.633
(cheering continues)

28:24.403 --> 28:27.173
DIANA: So, we are all
very eager to hear

28:27.206 --> 28:29.075
about your little performance.

28:29.108 --> 28:30.342
I was mediocre.

28:30.376 --> 28:31.844
My voice cracked twice,

28:31.878 --> 28:34.613
and my chords
were a little murky.

28:34.646 --> 28:36.248
But Jamal Lyon
thinks I'm gorgeous.

28:37.149 --> 28:38.517
(laughs)
Fabulous.

28:38.550 --> 28:39.886
Because we are.

28:39.919 --> 28:42.755
The DuBois twins are ready
for battle. Lyons beware.

28:42.789 --> 28:45.024
ANGELO: Well, knowing
Jamal as I do,

28:45.057 --> 28:49.028
I'm pretty sure this will be
one of our easier conquests.

28:49.061 --> 28:50.930
Angelo, do not be smug.

28:50.963 --> 28:53.966
The Lyon family
is formidable.

28:54.000 --> 28:56.936
However, I am confident
about Hakeem.

28:56.969 --> 28:58.437
So,

28:58.470 --> 28:59.972
here we go.

29:00.006 --> 29:01.040
Â¿Salud?

29:01.073 --> 29:04.143
ALL:
Salud.

29:04.176 --> 29:05.945
* Baby, it's you *

29:05.978 --> 29:07.446
* I'll always be
thinking of you *

29:07.479 --> 29:08.881
* I... *

29:08.915 --> 29:10.582
COOKIE: So, what you got
to tell us, boy?

29:10.616 --> 29:13.452
HAKEEM:
Dad, you killed it.
Thank you, son.

29:13.485 --> 29:16.322
Thank you, but who really killed
it was this mug right here.

29:16.355 --> 29:17.790
No, that's you, baby.
COOKIE:
Oh, yeah,

29:17.824 --> 29:19.158
both of y'all were good.
All you.

29:19.191 --> 29:20.626
Okay, look, look,
what do you have to tell us?

29:20.659 --> 29:21.627
Okay, so, look,

29:21.660 --> 29:22.862
Anika found Bella.

29:24.463 --> 29:26.765
What? Where?
Are you serious? Where? When?

29:26.799 --> 29:28.901
And, what-- have you seen her?
I seen her, Mom,

29:28.935 --> 29:30.169
I held her in my arms.

29:30.202 --> 29:31.603
I even got a picture of us.

29:32.872 --> 29:34.807
Boom.

29:34.841 --> 29:38.144
Oh, my God.
Oh, my God, it's amazing.

29:38.177 --> 29:39.145
COOKIE:
And she's okay?

29:39.178 --> 29:40.679
Where is she?
Wait, whose house is that?

29:40.712 --> 29:42.014
It's Anika's parents' house.

29:42.048 --> 29:43.850
She's there safe and sound
with them.

29:45.117 --> 29:46.452
This day
couldn't get better, man.

29:49.488 --> 29:51.123
* Give yourself
a round of applause... *

29:51.157 --> 29:53.359
*

29:53.392 --> 29:56.028
Hi, yes, this is Anika Calhoun.

29:56.062 --> 29:58.464
You guys-- no, no, no,
everything's divine.

29:58.497 --> 30:00.499
I was just wondering,
you guys wouldn't happen to have

30:00.532 --> 30:03.870
some, uh, hot sauce, would you?

30:03.903 --> 30:05.271
Fabulous.

30:05.304 --> 30:07.173
Yes, thank you, thank you.

30:07.206 --> 30:08.474
Bye-bye.

30:11.043 --> 30:12.278
(sighs)

30:12.311 --> 30:16.148
(cell phone rings)

30:16.182 --> 30:17.483
Hello?

30:17.516 --> 30:19.785
It's your future
ex-mother-in-law.

30:19.818 --> 30:21.653
Some more mail came for you.

30:21.687 --> 30:24.823
If you're still at the hotel,
I can just have it messengered.

30:24.857 --> 30:26.792
Yes, actually, can you send it
to The Peninsula

30:26.825 --> 30:28.895
in the penthouse suite?

30:28.928 --> 30:30.162
Thanks.

30:30.196 --> 30:32.098
Thank you.

30:44.376 --> 30:46.178
(knocks at door)

30:46.212 --> 30:47.579
Finally.

30:47.613 --> 30:49.315
Lord.

30:49.348 --> 30:51.583
How long's it take
to get some hot sauce in here?

30:56.588 --> 30:57.823
Anika Lyon?

30:57.856 --> 30:59.525
I prefer "Calhoun."

30:59.558 --> 31:02.361
You're under arrest
for the murder of Tariq Cousins.

31:02.394 --> 31:03.695
Excuse me?

31:03.729 --> 31:05.331
You have the right
to remain silent.

31:05.364 --> 31:07.199
Anything you say can
and will be used against you.

31:07.233 --> 31:08.567
You have the right
to an attorney.

31:08.600 --> 31:09.835
If you cannot
afford one,

31:09.868 --> 31:11.203
the court will
appoint one for you.

31:15.441 --> 31:18.244
*
(slot machines chiming)

31:18.277 --> 31:19.578
Hey, Loretha?

31:20.812 --> 31:22.548
Loretha.
Hey, Loretha...

31:22.581 --> 31:24.850
Oh, I know her.
COOKIE: Is that
Barry Hudson from Philly?

31:24.883 --> 31:27.386
Hey, is that Bar-- Barry?

31:27.419 --> 31:29.555
(laughs)
Oh, let him in.

31:29.588 --> 31:31.423
Let him in, Webb. Come back.
Guys, guys, let him in.

31:31.457 --> 31:33.892
Look at this. See? Hey.

31:33.926 --> 31:35.962
(Barry chuckling)

31:35.995 --> 31:37.429
COOKIE:
Barry, hey.
Hey.

31:37.463 --> 31:39.798
What are you
doing here?

31:39.831 --> 31:41.433
Oh, we're on vacation.

31:41.467 --> 31:42.734
Oh, my goodness,
have a seat.

31:42.768 --> 31:44.570
How are you, brother?
Good to see you.

31:44.603 --> 31:47.940
Uh, actually, uh,
celebrating a big milestone.

31:47.974 --> 31:49.608
Y'all want something to drink?

31:49.641 --> 31:51.743
No, no, no, no, no,
thank you, though.
(chuckles)

31:51.777 --> 31:53.745
This is my wife, Michelle.
Oh. Hi, how are you?

31:53.779 --> 31:55.281
Nice to meet you.
This is Cookie.
(chuckles)

31:55.314 --> 31:57.249
She saw that Lucious Lyon
was opening a show here.

31:57.283 --> 32:00.219
Uh, sold out,
but we got scalped tickets.

32:00.252 --> 32:02.388
She's a huge fan.

32:02.421 --> 32:04.156
She always teased
that I was

32:04.190 --> 32:05.992
confabulating when
I claimed I used to know you.

32:06.025 --> 32:07.459
Ah.
(Barry chuckles)
MICHELLE: Can you blame me?

32:07.493 --> 32:08.961
I mean, Barry isn't exactly
a hepcat.

32:08.995 --> 32:10.229
(laughs)

32:10.262 --> 32:11.797
Yeah, Barry knows us.

32:11.830 --> 32:14.766
I'm sure he wished
he never met us.

32:14.800 --> 32:16.802
Oh, come on, we were just
crazy kids, right?

32:16.835 --> 32:18.770
Everything worked out.

32:18.804 --> 32:21.473
I'm a doctor,
married to a doctor.

32:21.507 --> 32:23.009
Michelle and I had

32:23.042 --> 32:25.477
a nice, little family practice
out in Bala Cynwyd.

32:25.511 --> 32:27.113
"Had"? What happened?

32:27.146 --> 32:29.015
MICHELLE: Oh, well,
the big milestone

32:29.048 --> 32:30.782
that we're celebrating
is retirement.

32:30.816 --> 32:32.518
O-Our daughter, Sarah,
graduated from med school

32:32.551 --> 32:34.086
and joined the practice,

32:34.120 --> 32:36.122
and we just turned
the whole thing over to her.

32:36.155 --> 32:38.457
Your daughter's a doctor?
COOKIE:
Wow, that's amazing.

32:38.490 --> 32:39.691
Congratulations.
MICHELLE:
Thanks.

32:39.725 --> 32:41.027
BARRY:
So now we can just...

32:41.060 --> 32:42.794
cut loose,

32:42.828 --> 32:44.363
see the world,
enjoy each other.

32:46.898 --> 32:49.101
Anyway, um, here's my card.

32:49.135 --> 32:51.803
I know you've probably got
a million people to talk to,

32:51.837 --> 32:53.939
but maybe we can all have
dinner before we leave town.

32:53.972 --> 32:55.774
I'd like that.
We'd like that.

32:55.807 --> 32:57.476
Yeah, you know what? Let...

32:57.509 --> 32:59.278
why don't we take
a picture together?

32:59.311 --> 33:01.813
Oh. Oh, wow, that's nice
of you to... thank you.
(sniffles)

33:01.847 --> 33:03.015
Let's just break protocol.

33:03.049 --> 33:04.316
(laughs)
Appreciate it.

33:04.350 --> 33:05.684
Come on, y'all got scalped
tickets.
(laughs)

33:05.717 --> 33:06.952
You might as well
get a real picture.

33:06.985 --> 33:08.487
Oh, appreciate it.
There you go.

33:08.520 --> 33:09.821
Oh, good one, baby.

33:09.855 --> 33:11.357
Okay, good.
Thank you so much, really.

33:11.390 --> 33:13.292
No, no, thank y'all.
Thanks y'all for, uh,
having us come in.

33:13.325 --> 33:15.294
Yeah, thanks.

33:15.327 --> 33:17.163
It was such a pleasure
seeing you.
(chuckles)

33:17.196 --> 33:19.465
I can't believe
all these years.
You, too.

33:19.498 --> 33:21.833
Congratulations again.
(chuckles)
Thank you.

33:21.867 --> 33:24.002
Yeah.
My man.

33:24.036 --> 33:25.237
Pleasure seeing you again.

33:25.271 --> 33:26.672
Thank you.
Thank you so much.

33:26.705 --> 33:27.906
Y'all take care.
Thank you.

33:27.939 --> 33:29.575
Come on.

33:29.608 --> 33:31.510
Hey, man, I told you
we could see them.

33:31.543 --> 33:33.079
They're so sweet.
They're nice people.

33:33.112 --> 33:34.446
MICHELLE:
That's crazy.

33:36.448 --> 33:38.817
Wow.

33:38.850 --> 33:41.687
I'm not gonna lie...

33:41.720 --> 33:44.356
that kind of stirred up
my feelings.

33:46.192 --> 33:48.160
Did you see the way they were
holding hands with each other

33:48.194 --> 33:49.928
and looking at each other?

33:49.961 --> 33:51.897
Mm-hmm.
Say to hell with it.

33:51.930 --> 33:53.399
Why don't we just take a page

33:53.432 --> 33:55.601
right out of Barry
and-and Michelle's book?

33:57.203 --> 33:59.571
I want to see the world
with you, Cook.

33:59.605 --> 34:02.241
I want to write
a new page in our story,

34:02.274 --> 34:05.911
far away from the backbiting
and the drama.

34:05.944 --> 34:08.914
You created that drama
by pitting your sons

34:08.947 --> 34:10.449
against each other.

34:12.451 --> 34:15.887
I created it, but together
we can uncreate it.

34:15.921 --> 34:19.925
What you doing down
there, Grandpa?

34:19.958 --> 34:21.793
Better get off them
arthritic knees.

34:21.827 --> 34:23.762
(laughs)
(smooches)
What do you say?

34:23.795 --> 34:25.131
What do I say what?

34:25.164 --> 34:27.699
(chuckles)
Say yes.

34:27.733 --> 34:29.401
See the world with me.

34:29.435 --> 34:32.104
I say your ass need
to have a ring.

34:32.138 --> 34:34.940
I can buy you
a whole jewelry store.

34:34.973 --> 34:36.642
(both laugh)

34:39.478 --> 34:41.947
COOKIE: Andre.

34:44.250 --> 34:45.984
I've been looking
for you all day.

34:46.017 --> 34:47.719
Where the hell you been?
Shine told me you backing out...

34:47.753 --> 34:49.555
Shut up. Shut up, boy. We not
gonna mention that no more.

34:49.588 --> 34:51.590
Hey, y'all,
look who I found.

34:51.623 --> 34:52.991
JAMAL: Uh-oh, Dre.
HAKEEM: Hey.

34:53.024 --> 34:54.593
What's up?
Hey, what's up?
There you are.

34:54.626 --> 34:56.462
Bro, bro, what's up, man?
ANDRE:
What's up?

34:58.029 --> 35:00.432
Listen up, y'all, um,

35:00.466 --> 35:02.234
your mother and I
have something

35:02.268 --> 35:03.635
we want to share
with you three.

35:03.669 --> 35:04.836
We made a decision.

35:04.870 --> 35:06.172
What kind of decision?

35:06.205 --> 35:08.307
A big one.

35:08.340 --> 35:13.179
We have decided to step down
from the day-to-day operations

35:13.212 --> 35:14.713
of Empire.

35:16.948 --> 35:18.517
Hold on, wait,
is one of y'all sick?

35:18.550 --> 35:19.851
No.
No.

35:19.885 --> 35:21.587
(chuckles)
The opposite.

35:21.620 --> 35:24.823
(chuckles)
We are actually
very well and of sound mind,

35:24.856 --> 35:26.592
and now that you've
got Bella back...

35:26.625 --> 35:27.959
And that bitch is gone--

35:27.993 --> 35:29.461
and I don't want to ever
hear her name again.

35:29.495 --> 35:30.862
(chuckling)

35:30.896 --> 35:33.665
(laughs)
Okay. Forgive me.

35:33.699 --> 35:35.967
Um, we just realized

35:36.001 --> 35:38.870
that life is too short.

35:38.904 --> 35:40.972
Mm.
And we want to spend
the rest of it

35:41.006 --> 35:44.976
doing something we fantasized
about when we were kids.

35:45.010 --> 35:46.044
Being happy.

35:46.077 --> 35:47.145
Being happy.

35:47.179 --> 35:48.314
(chuckles)

35:48.347 --> 35:50.015
And, Jamal,
you been talking forever

35:50.048 --> 35:52.818
about us breaking the cycle.

35:52.851 --> 35:54.019
Well, it's time.

35:55.354 --> 35:58.957
And it's time that I...

35:58.990 --> 36:01.360
do something I should've
done years ago.

36:05.531 --> 36:06.598
What's this?

36:11.069 --> 36:13.539
The keys to the kingdom,
literally.

36:15.040 --> 36:16.408
Those are my office keys.

36:17.909 --> 36:19.545
Thirsty is gonna have
some papers drawn up

36:19.578 --> 36:23.715
for the board's approval,
but it's all yours, Dre.

36:25.217 --> 36:26.685
Mine?
COOKIE:
Yes, baby.

36:26.718 --> 36:28.687
We should've done this
a long time ago.

36:30.021 --> 36:32.023
Hakeem and-and
Jamal are artists,

36:32.057 --> 36:33.392
with huge

36:33.425 --> 36:36.061
careers ahead of them

36:36.094 --> 36:38.997
and they need a strong company
to stand behind them.

36:39.030 --> 36:42.033
And, baby, XStream,

36:42.067 --> 36:44.403
Empire XStream,
that was all you.

36:44.436 --> 36:45.904
This Vegas deal

36:45.937 --> 36:47.339
was all you.

36:47.373 --> 36:48.707
You are the one

36:48.740 --> 36:50.776
to take Empire
to the next level.

36:54.713 --> 36:57.249
Said that I was a liability.

36:59.084 --> 37:00.586
I was scared of you.

37:01.820 --> 37:03.121
Because I'd grown up

37:03.154 --> 37:04.723
with a mother
that had your issues

37:04.756 --> 37:06.925
and so they
became issues for me.

37:06.958 --> 37:09.528
But I've found out
that condition

37:09.561 --> 37:12.097
that you were born with,
it gave you a brain

37:12.130 --> 37:14.766
that can outmaneuver
any man on the chessboard,

37:14.800 --> 37:16.067
including myself.

37:17.969 --> 37:20.572
And you can control it
when you have the support

37:20.606 --> 37:23.642
of your family around you.
That's right.

37:23.675 --> 37:26.578
And when you're taking
care of yourself, son,

37:26.612 --> 37:28.747
you're unstoppable.

37:28.780 --> 37:32.618
And I want y'all to make sure
y'all give him the support

37:32.651 --> 37:34.886
that he needs.
That's right.

37:34.920 --> 37:37.088
You deserve it, bro.

37:37.122 --> 37:38.424
Congrats.

37:38.457 --> 37:40.158
Y'all already know.

37:40.191 --> 37:41.993
The boss.

37:42.027 --> 37:43.995
(chuckles)
Congrats, man.

37:46.465 --> 37:48.166
LUCIOUS:
Look, your mother and I

37:48.199 --> 37:50.402
want you to know know
how very proud we are

37:50.436 --> 37:53.939
to have you
as our firstborn.

37:55.374 --> 37:57.976
Lucious, just tell
the boy you love him.

37:58.009 --> 38:00.245
The hell out of here.
Ugh.

38:00.278 --> 38:01.413
(laughs)

38:01.447 --> 38:03.415
Well, look, I'm-a fly
back on the jet tonight.

38:03.449 --> 38:05.684
I want to get back so
I can be ready with Bella.

38:05.717 --> 38:07.986
COOKIE:
All right.

38:08.019 --> 38:09.421
Give her a hug for me.
Kiss her for me.
(chuckles)

38:09.455 --> 38:10.856
Wait for me 'cause I'm-a
roll with you, a'ight?

38:10.889 --> 38:13.124
HAKEEM:
Hurry up.
(stammers)
You have a show to do.

38:13.158 --> 38:14.793
When Cookie Met Lucious
is officially dropping.

38:14.826 --> 38:16.161
I know, but we a hit.

38:16.194 --> 38:17.463
(both laugh)

38:17.496 --> 38:18.664
Look, I'll be back on Sunday.

38:18.697 --> 38:20.632
I just want to spend
the weekend in New York.

38:20.666 --> 38:23.134
Ah, yeah, I met somebody.
Dang, all up in my business.

38:23.168 --> 38:24.603
Mm-hmm.
All up in here.

38:24.636 --> 38:25.771
Uh-huh.

38:25.804 --> 38:28.840
It's all good...
Shine!

38:28.874 --> 38:30.776
Where's Franco?

38:30.809 --> 38:32.611
He's not answering
his phone.

38:32.644 --> 38:34.446
Franco left already.
I got the app right here.

38:34.480 --> 38:35.614
Well, give it to me.
I'm calling it off.

38:35.647 --> 38:37.148
Come again.

38:37.182 --> 38:40.285
My family just handed me
control of the company, Shine.

38:40.318 --> 38:41.487
Okay?

38:41.520 --> 38:43.154
I promise you
you won't be left out.

38:43.188 --> 38:44.390
Okay, Lucious just
mounted a hit show.

38:44.423 --> 38:45.524
You get a piece of that, too.
Give me the app.

38:45.557 --> 38:47.292
Give me the phone.
Come on, give me the app.

38:47.325 --> 38:48.794
Shine, give me...

38:48.827 --> 38:50.161
Man, keep your promises.

38:50.195 --> 38:52.197
It's so funny.

38:52.230 --> 38:54.132
You always saying
we from the same place,

38:54.165 --> 38:55.634
but we ain't the same!

38:55.667 --> 38:57.002
There's a code.

38:57.035 --> 38:58.236
And the code says you
can't bring it back

38:58.269 --> 39:00.539
when the bullet leaves the gun.

39:00.572 --> 39:02.173
You started this.
I'm-a finish it.

39:02.207 --> 39:03.809
Now get him out of here.
You'll have to shoot me.

39:03.842 --> 39:04.976
Get off of me!

39:05.010 --> 39:06.277
Pop!

39:08.414 --> 39:09.381
LUCIOUS:
Let's go to Bermuda.

39:09.415 --> 39:10.716
(Cookie laughs)

39:10.749 --> 39:12.050
We talked about that
when we were kids.

39:12.083 --> 39:13.719
Bermuda is played
out, child.

39:13.752 --> 39:15.320
You have to take me
to Turks and Caicos.

39:15.353 --> 39:17.689
Well, then why don't I
just buy us our own island?

39:17.723 --> 39:19.658
COOKIE:
Oh, you think you slick?

39:19.691 --> 39:20.859
You think you can
get in my drawers

39:20.892 --> 39:22.394
by saying something
slick like that?

39:22.428 --> 39:24.262
No, I want to get
in your heart.
Oh. (chuckles)

39:24.295 --> 39:26.364
Come on.
(laughs)

39:26.398 --> 39:27.533
ANDRE: Pop!

39:27.566 --> 39:28.700
Ma!

39:28.734 --> 39:29.768
What, boy?

39:29.801 --> 39:30.869
ANDRE: Move!

39:30.902 --> 39:32.370
Get away from the car!

39:32.404 --> 39:33.405
Why?

39:33.439 --> 39:34.440
LUCIOUS: Go!

39:41.079 --> 39:43.114
Ma!

39:43.148 --> 39:45.116
Dad!

39:50.221 --> 39:52.458
No, it's lit.
No, no, no, no.

39:54.926 --> 39:57.763
(echoing):
Lucious!

39:57.796 --> 40:00.065
No!

40:09.274 --> 40:11.677
(heart monitor beeping)

40:14.846 --> 40:16.982
"To my friend, Lucious Lyon.

40:17.015 --> 40:19.818
"I can't wait until
you come back roaring.

40:19.851 --> 40:21.052
"Best wishes

40:21.086 --> 40:22.888
"for a speedy recovery.

40:22.921 --> 40:25.090
All my love, Stevie."

40:25.123 --> 40:26.992
JAMAL:
Dad, that's amazing, man.

40:27.025 --> 40:29.160
It's Stevie, huh?
Yeah.

40:29.194 --> 40:31.262
He's in a coma.
He can't hear nothing.

40:31.296 --> 40:32.263
Shut up, boy.

40:32.297 --> 40:35.100
WOMAN: He can hear
a lot more than you think.

40:37.135 --> 40:40.305
I've had patients
in your father's condition

40:40.338 --> 40:41.840
come out of comas after months,

40:41.873 --> 40:43.509
actually, sometimes
even years,

40:43.542 --> 40:45.310
and recall everything.

40:46.344 --> 40:47.746
So, you might want
to watch what you say.

40:47.779 --> 40:49.014
Can you please make sure

40:49.047 --> 40:50.816
that those scans that Dr. West
ordered are loaded in?

40:50.849 --> 40:52.050
Yes, ma'am.
Thank you.

40:54.285 --> 40:57.355
So, it's, uh, story time.

40:57.388 --> 40:59.658
Tonight I was gonna read
the short story by Borges,

40:59.691 --> 41:01.159
the one you said that he loved.

41:01.192 --> 41:03.228
Yeah.

41:08.534 --> 41:10.368
Dwight.

41:16.842 --> 41:19.344
(whispering):
Dwight.

41:30.822 --> 41:32.558
Dwight.

41:33.491 --> 41:34.993
Dwight.

41:36.327 --> 41:37.996
Uh.
(clears throat)

41:40.999 --> 41:42.534
You can go.

41:42.568 --> 41:45.336
Oh, no, we're not going nowhere
no time soon.

41:45.370 --> 41:47.539
You mind telling us
why you sent that nurse

41:47.573 --> 41:50.408
for the scans?
Mrs. Lyon, you know
that I am not at liberty

41:50.441 --> 41:52.711
to discuss his test results.

41:52.744 --> 41:55.581
Okay, well, then are you at
liberty to lose your damn job?
Ma.

41:55.614 --> 41:57.583
Because... no, we are
paying for all of this.
JAMAL: Okay, but calm down.

41:57.616 --> 41:59.585
She's just trying to help, Mom.
You supposed to do
what I tell you to do.

41:59.618 --> 42:01.352
JAMAL:
Just calm down.
It's okay.

42:01.386 --> 42:02.888
She's just helping out.
(clears throat)

42:02.921 --> 42:04.656
It's all right.
She doesn't need to calm down.

42:04.690 --> 42:06.391
I understand.
This is very stressful.

42:06.424 --> 42:08.026
Yeah, I'm stressed

42:08.059 --> 42:09.194
and the last thing
you should be doing

42:09.227 --> 42:10.395
is telling me how stressed I am.

42:10.428 --> 42:11.830
It's rude.
JAMAL: Ma.

42:11.863 --> 42:13.231
ANDRE:
Mom, let's-let's just go.

42:13.264 --> 42:14.332
COOKIE:
You know what?

42:14.365 --> 42:17.402
(sighs)
All right.

42:17.435 --> 42:19.104
Give me my stuff, boy.

42:19.137 --> 42:22.273
Look, I know you some kind of
special nurse and all of that,

42:22.307 --> 42:24.075
but it's been three months

42:24.109 --> 42:25.410
and he still look
like a vegetable,

42:25.443 --> 42:27.078
so maybe you ain't
so damn special.

42:27.112 --> 42:28.880
Come on, Dad.
We'll see you tomorrow.

42:28.914 --> 42:31.549
COOKIE:
Yes, you will see me tomorrow.

42:32.584 --> 42:33.785
Mom, Mom.

42:33.819 --> 42:36.421
Look, Ma.
Come here.

42:36.454 --> 42:37.555
What?
Dad.

42:37.589 --> 42:38.924
(stammers)
I'm-I'm not tripping.

42:38.957 --> 42:40.291
H-His eyes were open.
They're closed now,

42:40.325 --> 42:41.492
but I swear,
they-they fluttered.

42:42.628 --> 42:43.662
Pop, can you hear us?
HAKEEM: Dad.

42:45.130 --> 42:46.998
Lucious?

42:50.235 --> 42:51.236
Ooh! There he is.

42:51.269 --> 42:52.738
Lucious. (gasps)
Lucious!
Yeah.

42:52.771 --> 42:54.940
Lucious! Lucious.
JAMAL (muffled):
Yo, what's up, Dad?

42:54.973 --> 42:57.876
Come on, man, what's up?
(muffled): Hi, Dad.
It's Hakeem, Dad.

42:57.909 --> 42:59.778
COOKIE (muffled): Welcome back.
JAMAL (muffled): Wait, Ma,
he's trying to say something.

42:59.811 --> 43:02.347
Cookie, yes. Cookie.

43:04.415 --> 43:05.784
Who are you?

43:05.817 --> 43:07.052
Cookie.

43:07.085 --> 43:08.153
It's us.

43:09.487 --> 43:10.588
Yeah, we're here.

43:10.622 --> 43:11.957
HAKEEM:
Yeah, Dad.

43:11.990 --> 43:13.024
It's Hakeem.

43:14.492 --> 43:16.227
(echoing):
It's okay.

43:16.261 --> 43:18.630
It's your family.
JAMAL:
Yeah, man, it's all right.

43:18.664 --> 43:20.098
We're here.
HAKEEM: Yeah.

43:22.701 --> 43:24.335
Who?

43:59.705 --> 44:00.872
Yeah.

44:00.906 --> 44:02.874
Captioned by
Media Access Group at WGBH

44:05.476 --> 44:07.145
ANNOUNCER: You've just
watched Empire.

44:07.178 --> 44:09.915
Now here are a few more shows
to check out from Fox.

44:11.850 --> 44:14.385
Mommy has to go
out of town for work.

44:15.921 --> 44:17.555
Something
ain't right here.

44:17.588 --> 44:19.825
The department
is obviously corrupt.

44:19.858 --> 44:21.827
-I understand how you feel.
-No, you don't.

44:21.860 --> 44:24.662
My son is dead.

44:24.696 --> 44:26.732
-MAN:
You should go back to DC.
-(grunts)

44:26.765 --> 44:28.800
Their threats
don't faze me.

44:28.834 --> 44:31.002
This some sort
of game to you?

44:31.036 --> 44:33.271
ASHE: We're taking on
an entire sheriff's department.

44:35.540 --> 44:37.642
Nobody comes out
of this clean.

